# CODEOWNERS for adversarial-review
#
# GitHub automatically requests review from owners listed here when a PR
# changes the matching path. Owners are also the implicit review queue if
# the branch protection rule "require review from Code Owners" is ever
# enabled (it currently is not — see branch protection on `main`).
#
# This file is intentionally upstream-specific for
# laceyenterprises/adversarial-review. Fork operators MUST replace the
# owners below with accounts or teams that have write access in their fork
# before enabling "require review from Code Owners"; otherwise GitHub cannot
# request a meaningful code-owner review.
#
# Patterns are evaluated last-match-wins. Keep the catch-all at the top.

